  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2 class="c-heading-h2">Choose from our range of active holidays across Europe</h2>
<p><span>Variety is the spice of life and a summer holiday means something different to everybody. Whether you’re an active adventurer walking and cycling in the mountains, looking to relax by the lakes, or after a family holiday that everyone can enjoy, Inghams summer holidays have the flexibility and diversity to make your dream summer holiday possible.</span></p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Walking holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092749/walker-lake-314x193.jpg" alt="Walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/c3fcef3e109541919ca63b4ac79198de" /></p>
<p>Discover a walkers paradise on a self-guided holiday. We've chosen our<span> resorts for their culture and endless activities, so you can see more, do more and discover more. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Rail holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092750/switzerland-rail-314x193.jpg" alt="Rail holidays" data-udi="umb://media/c7dcf1d8f2784c5cbc5207ae556b9b02" /></p>
<p><span>Sit back, relax and enjoy Europe's most breathtaking landscapes on a rail holiday through Europe. Travel from the UK to Switzerland, France and Italy. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Multi-centre holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092751/italy-town-314x193.jpg" alt="Multicentre Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/8de847059d8446fd9f9c6bfec30572de" /></p>
<p><span>Why go on holiday to one country or region, when you could visit two, or even three? Our carefully crafted itineraries are designed to help you explore the best of each destination.</span></p>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Family holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092752/lake-garda-family-sailing-boats-314x193.jpg" alt="Family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/68b971209bb84977bddadeea635482df" /></p>
<p>Our family holidays offer the perfect blend of activity, fun and relaxation for the whole family. Discover our handpicked family-friendly resorts and accommodation.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Singles holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092753/women-by-lake-italy-314x193.jpg" alt="Singles holidays" data-udi="umb://media/3942e3fedf254325a2481d38c44291c8" /></p>
<p>Designed to help you experience the thrill of travelling solo, while still being able to meet like-minded people, browse our solo holidays with no single supplements. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>City Breaks</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092754/venice-314x193.jpg" alt="City Breaks" data-udi="umb://media/e4e83166087f460b8b8529544761d71d" /></p>
<p>Explore the incredible cities of Italy including Venice, Rome and Florence, and why not include a short stay as part of a tour or multicentre holiday. </p>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Lakes and Mountains</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092755/austria-town-lake-view-314x193.jpg" alt="Lakes and Mountains Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/f76ea922d24d4ff6bd6333c4f2f59d3a" /></p>
<p><span>From quaint waterfront towns to mountain villages, experience unmissable scenery and adventures across Europe's lakes and mountains. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Italy Coastal Holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092756/puglia-sea-town-314x193.jpg" alt="Italy coastal holidays" data-udi="umb://media/b503c3ab217546d98ec8282548250a0d" /></p>
<p>Italy offers incredible coastal walking opportunities, perfect for soaking up the scenery along the way - from Cinque Terre to Puglia and Tuscany. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Cycling holidays</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092757/austria-cyclist-314x193.jpg" alt="Cycling holidays" data-udi="umb://media/bc66ab4ebbb549bf873ac5c7a12898a6" /></p>
<p><span>From gentle cycle paths through flower filled meadows to steep trails crossing the mountains, soak up the scenery, local culture and wildlife at your own pace by bike. </span></p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="g4">
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
